Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}sure{\i0} you're okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.46,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.20,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{H-}Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.46,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.60,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear that sound.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna! Wait for us!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, look.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna! Come back!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Past that point is—
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.26,0:01:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a mysterious sound.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.90,0:01:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sounded like grains of sand \Nscraping against each other...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like the sound of Manaka-san's heart pounding,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just as the tide pounds against the shore.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shioshishio...
