Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.12,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if people were out \Nand sleepwalking or something,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be creepy.{Zombie Apocalypse Underwater \o/}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.94,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the place where Hikari, \NKaname-san, Chisaki-san, and Manaka-san lived.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet somehow...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems to be working.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The light is on.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they can use this \Nto measure all sorts of things,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the salinity and the flow of the tide.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what it's really like.{the village wasnt always like this}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go look for Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's old man Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he was trying \Nto guard the place...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we were all told \Nbefore the hibernation
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that we should be relaxing at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His back's probably gonna hurt \Nwhen he wakes up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be back to normal \Nas soon as he wakes up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he will.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here I am, in the place I always \Ndreamed of visiting,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.77,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck are you acting so scared?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, they're just hibernating!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at everyone like that is really rude!{Hikari pls. stfu.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What, do you think they're \Nall dead or something?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.43,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I go home for a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.99,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go calm down \Nbefore we look for Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't calm down,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling I'll be too worked up \Nand make an even bigger fool of myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself feel a bit worked up.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back as soon as possible, \Nso could you wait for us here?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wander off.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my first time seeing Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.54,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari and Kaname are probably seeing this \NShioshishio for the first time as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't mean anything by it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... they really {\i1}are{\i0} just sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.04,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just hibernation, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko} and the adults \Nweren't just lying to us, were they?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, \Nwe wouldn't have woken up either, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm just being selfish.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how Miuna's birth \Nmother was from the sea?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.80,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just wanted her to see how pretty it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.76,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shioshishio that belonged \Nto Miuna's mom... and to us.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the world I always imagined,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that unknown world...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with unknown roads
