Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since the world from my imagination \Nwas always so bright,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}since it always shined so brilliantly...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was caught off guard.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man Hayakawa's keeping guard.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He always gets super serious \Nabout dumb stuff like that,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but just look at him now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.95,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, did you know you have a grandkid?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just Miuna, but a little boy too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Akira.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's almost four now.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.12,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, I only found out the other day too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you know what his favorite game is?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that {replace}"kancho"{"Up your butt"} game I used to play.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what are we gonna do with that kid?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like he's not cute or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, I guess he {\i1}is{\i0} kinda cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari says he looks like me when I was younger,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not like I would know.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was hoping you could meet him \Nand tell me your opinion... or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I just say Manaka-san's name?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we only managed \Nto come back 'cause of Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She can breathe underwater now.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty surprising, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, she heard some weird sound,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and she followed it and led us here.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.57,0:11:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to show her the real Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's thanks to her \Nthat we were even able to come back here.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.48,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. I never did come out and say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for bringing us here."
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.76,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't said that to her yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the Shioshishio I always dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.63,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.24\blur0.6\frz345.9\frx0\fry6\c&HFFE378&\pos(630,221)}2nd Year
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.63,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, I acted like that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.63,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\an4\blur0.8\fscx32\fscy32\c&H725C39&\b1\alpha&H10&\pos(837,201)}Entrance \NCeremony
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.63,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H765C38&\fscx36\fscy36\frz0.9542\b1\pos(880,469)\alpha&H10&}New \NStudents
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and wound up hurting Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.40,Some Boring Chalk #59,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.05\blur1\c&H150E04&\frx0\fry6\b1\1a&H5F&\frz5.914\fscx142\fscy137\move(335.98,-112.33,336,114,27,1279)}You haven't grown \Nmuch, Manaka.\N{\fax-0.16}You haven't either, Hii!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's here.
