Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I specifically told her not to wander off.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}sure{\i0} you looked everywhere?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to argue!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for her.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh.}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember seeing those.{professional trackers}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Miuna, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a scale, I suppose.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A scale? Like the scale of a fish?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That kind of a scale.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the school under the sea any fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So before, that was...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shioshishio's a wonderful place, \Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I was looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That's odd.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.52,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not come here in search of that?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.90,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a god, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a mere scale.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me where Manaka-san is!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you were {\i1}truly{\i0} looking for,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.08,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can tell you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.86,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for is Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.64,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying to the face of the servant of a god... \NWhat an audacious child you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We told you to stay right there!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.76,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san is nearby.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just met God.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"God"?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the sea god?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's talking about {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he didn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.00,0:16:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since he's the protector \Nof this village, you may be right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.24,0:16:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to run and play around here \Nwhen we were in grade school,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't remember ever seeing this place.{but all this is unfamiliar}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all of these...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooden Maidens?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.20,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These are probably all the Wooden Maidens \Nthat were sacrificed over the years...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every last one.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A graveyard of Wooden Maidens...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that in the middle?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.81,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan, wait here.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.78,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember what Tsumugu said?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.38,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't force people who \Nare sleeping to wake up.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.14,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows what kind of \Neffect it may have on them.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.01,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} what you were looking for.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.50,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I just wanted to come to Shioshishio."
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those words are nothing more than a child's fib.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.28,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When something appears, \Nsomething else is lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.56,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this, everything \Nbalances out in the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, what are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us are waiting for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a Wooden Maiden,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.92,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so you shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san's trying to wake up...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.87,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This sound!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Ena's coming off.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's losing her Ena!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is something like this happening?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.61,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is messed up!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If Manaka loses her Ena, she'll die!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta get Manaka to the shore.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't, she's gonna die!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn away for a second.{you've been staring at her naked body the whole time, but now that i'm gonna cover her, you should look away}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.57,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.84,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all this because the sea god is angry?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're taking Manaka back?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I care!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari! Not that way!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound is coming from over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
